## 8. Portfolio-Level Planning (Separate Artifact)

Everything above operates on one feature at a time. When you're planning a Program Increment across multiple features and teams against a fixed end date, that's a different kind of problem — fitting a portfolio of dependent work into limited team capacity — and it's covered separately in **Part 3 of this document**. It consumes the dependency commitment outcomes from the `dependency-firm-ask` skill and the sized, tagged stories from the `story-creation` skill as its inputs, and refuses to produce a schedule when those inputs are too rough to plan against.
